Ingredients Apple cider Spiced rum Fresh lemon juice Apple kombucha Cinnamon sticks Apple slices (optional) Preparations •Combine ½ cup of apple cider, ½ cup spiced rum, and 2 teaspoons lemon juice in a cocktail shaker over ice; •Shake until chilled, or about 30 seconds. •Pour over large ice cubes into two rocks glasses. •Repeat with remaining apple cider, rum, and lemon juice. •Add ¼ cup apple kombucha to each glass. •Garnish each with 1 cinnamon stick, and apple slices, if desired.